an, Ngô Văn Độ chi hậu bổ - 送進士阮文珊吳文度之候補</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/author-lfkyiRMg6zwt6_eiwas6Yg">Vũ Phạm Khải</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tr%C3%B9ng-du-H%C3%A0-th%E1%BB%8B-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-fs0qfA5VJ3iyWHk6qIpoag">Trùng du Hà thị kỳ 1 - 重遊何氏其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-qu%C3%A2n/poem-poKMVsKTu5nOsOOtpFmCOA">Tương quân - 湘君</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Xa-c%C3%B4ng-4/poem-kWNsjiJ4XCnJbMLspXYlEA">Xa công 4 - 車攻 4</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
